225
00:14:52.182 --> 00:14:53.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>說清楚就好了唄？</c.traditionalchinese>

226
00:14:53.851 --> 00:14:55.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
