227
00:14:55.895 --> 00:14:58.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>乾脆說咱們是情侶不就得了？</c.traditionalchinese>

228
00:15:03.068 --> 00:15:05.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
