235
00:15:26.926 --> 00:15:29.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>那個漂亮小妞是誰，又是怎麼回事？</c.traditionalchinese>

236
00:15:30.721 --> 00:15:33.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>生意上的合作關係，我們一起行商</c.traditionalchinese>

237
00:15:34.808 --> 00:15:35.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>生意？</c.traditionalchinese>

238
00:15:36.018 --> 00:15:38.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>在帕茲歐的米隆商行</c.traditionalchinese>

239
00:15:39.021 --> 00:15:41.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
