250
00:16:16.266 --> 00:16:20.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.traditionalchinese>再說，《聖經》上也說</c.traditionalchinese>

251
00:16:20.187 --> 00:16:22.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
